            <abstract obkms_id="dea86fcc-19a8-4506-913c-c29480d47fd1">
                <label>Abstract</label>
                <p>Five new supraspecific taxa of Scapania are proposed, <italic><tp:taxon-name obkms_id="37ed9156-7f3a-4fe0-a500-5d410537634f">Scapania</tp:taxon-name></italic> subg. <italic><tp:taxon-name obkms_id="f04d74dd-d111-40d3-bd64-e072da39eab9">Gracilidae</tp:taxon-name></italic>, <italic><tp:taxon-name obkms_id="76430a2d-8184-47ef-9b92-ab679a13397a">Scapania</tp:taxon-name></italic> subg. <italic><tp:taxon-name obkms_id="c184aaac-f669-44b0-8a68-7ff261c62bb2">Pseudomacrodiplophyllum</tp:taxon-name></italic>, <italic><tp:taxon-name obkms_id="405f852f-9b73-4719-aae5-ec36fce09d08">Scapania</tp:taxon-name></italic> sect. <italic><tp:taxon-name obkms_id="1bdf1f6b-2f90-46e7-b8c0-db4b8d2cc91f">Americanae</tp:taxon-name></italic>, <italic><tp:taxon-name obkms_id="e354e9cb-3f29-4e53-af22-b9d0f4816912">Scapania</tp:taxon-name></italic> sect. <italic><tp:taxon-name obkms_id="bac653de-360d-4cbc-a5d5-a3eb1bd84f23">Hyperboreae</tp:taxon-name></italic>, and <italic><tp:taxon-name obkms_id="f42765aa-ed81-42ac-905e-1297ce573c57">Scapania</tp:taxon-name></italic> sect. <italic><tp:taxon-name obkms_id="64e42209-a515-494a-a0c8-337270d4331f">Simmonsia</tp:taxon-name></italic>.</p>
            </abstract>
